IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY
 ORDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION
 NOTICE OF MOTION 2334 OF 2005
 IN
 CONTEMPT PETITION NO. 170 OF 1999
 IN
 SUIT NO. 38 OF 1978
 The New India Assurance Co. Ltd. .. Petitioners
 Versus
 M/s. J.S. Khanna & Co. & Ors. .. Respondents
 Mr.Raj Patel i/b Hariani & Co. for the Petitioners
 Mr.P.V. Palan i/b S.M. Kazi for the Respondent Nos. 17, 18.
 Ms. S.R. Moghe i/b Mehta & Girdharilal for Respondent
 Nos. 4, 6F, 6I.
 CORAM : S.K. SHAH, J.
 DATED : 2ND SEPTEMBER, 2005
 P.C.-
 1. Learned Counsel for the Respondent Nos. 17 and 18 has
 taken out this Notice of Motion. He requests for allowing
 the Notice of Motion to be withdrawn with liberty to file a
 Review Petition.
 2. Notice of Motion No. 2334 of 2005 is allowed to be
 withdrawn.
 3. Notice of Motion No. 2334 of 2005 stands dismissed as
 withdrawn.
 [S.K.SHAH, J.]
